04T22:59:13Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Support for the Visual Studio 2017 linker was added with PR #38584, and I guess that `rustc` now works either with the Community or the Professional or the Enterprise releases (see comparison [here](https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/vs/compare/)). However that PR does not cover [Visual Studio Express 2017](https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/vs/express/), whose linker is located at `c:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Visual Studio\\2017\\WDExpress\\VC\\Tools\\MSVC\\14.12.25827\\bin\\Hostx86\\x64\\link.exe`.\r\n\r\nIn order for `rustc` to find the Visual Studio Express 2017 linker I need to run `c:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Visual Studio\\2017\\WDExpress\\VC\\Auxiliary\\Build\\vcvarsx86_amd64.bat`.\r\n\r\nI'm on Windows 7, running `rustc` version 1.28.0 (stable).", "closed_by": {"login": "lucatrv", "id": 8380499, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjgzODA0OTk=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8380499?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv", "html_url": "https://github.com/lucatrv", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lucatrv/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/53474/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "e